{"ja447:0.1":"Jataka ","ja447:0.2":"Dasakanipata ","ja447:0.3":"Catudvaravagga ","ja447:0.4":"9. Mahadhammapalajataka ","ja447:1.1":"“Kim te vatam kim pana brahmacariyam, ","ja447:1.2":"Kissa sucinnassa ayam vipako; ","ja447:1.3":"Akkhahi me brahmana etamattham, ","ja447:1.4":"Kasma nu tumham dahara na miyyare”. ","ja447:2.1":"“Dhammam carama na musa bhanama, ","ja447:2.2":"Papani kammani parivajjayama; ","ja447:2.3":"Anariyam parivajjemu sabbam, ","ja447:2.4":"Tasma hi amham dahara na miyyare. ","ja447:3.1":"Sunoma dhammam asatam satanca, ","ja447:3.2":"Na capi dhammam asatam rocayama; ","ja447:3.3":"Hitva asante na jahama sante, ","ja447:3.4":"Tasma hi amham dahara na miyyare. ","ja447:4.1":"Pubbeva dana sumana bhavama, ","ja447:4.2":"Dadampi ve attamana bhavama; ","ja447:4.3":"Datvapi ve nanutappama paccha, ","ja447:4.4":"Tasma hi amham dahara na miyyare. ","ja447:5.1":"Samane mayam brahmane addhike ca, ","ja447:5.2":"Vanibbake yacanake dalidde; ","ja447:5.3":"Annena panena abhitappayama, ","ja447:5.4":"Tasma hi amham dahara na miyyare. ","ja447:6.1":"Mayanca bhariyam natikkamama, ","ja447:6.2":"Amhe ca bhariya natikkamanti; ","ja447:6.3":"Annatra tahi brahmacariyam carama, ","ja447:6.4":"Tasma hi amham dahara na miyyare. ","ja447:7.1":"Panatipata viramama sabbe, ","ja447:7.2":"Loke adinnam parivajjayama; ","ja447:7.3":"Amajjapa nopi musa bhanama, ","ja447:7.4":"Tasma hi amham dahara na miyyare. ","ja447:8.1":"Etasu ve jayare suttamasu, ","ja447:8.2":"Medhavino honti pahutapanna; ","ja447:8.3":"Bahussuta vedaguno ca honti, ","ja447:8.4":"Tasma hi amham dahara na miyyare. ","ja447:9.1":"Mata pita ca bhagini bhataro ca, ","ja447:9.2":"Putta ca dara ca mayanca sabbe; ","ja447:9.3":"Dhammam carama paralokahetu, ","ja447:9.4":"Tasma hi amham dahara na miyyare. ","ja447:10.1":"Dasa ca dasyo anujivino ca, ","ja447:10.2":"Paricaraka kammakara ca sabbe; ","ja447:10.3":"Dhammam caranti paralokahetu, ","ja447:10.4":"Tasma hi amham dahara na miyyare”. ","ja447:11.1":"“Dhammo have rakkhati dhammacarim, ","ja447:11.2":"Dhammo sucinno sukhamavahati; ","ja447:11.3":"Esanisamso dhamme sucinne, ","ja447:11.4":"Na duggatim gacchati dhammacari. ","ja447:12.1":"Dhammo have rakkhati dhammacarim, ","ja447:12.2":"Chattam mahantam viya vassakale; ","ja447:12.3":"Dhammena gutto mama dhammapalo, ","ja447:12.4":"Annassa atthini sukhi kumaro”ti. ","ja447:13.1":"Mahadhammapalajatakam navamam. "}